Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:49.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:53.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:57.87,Default - flashback,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just get a chance, I can make \Nany problem disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:10.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:15.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:45.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ram...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:49.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Petra...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:55.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emi... lia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.40,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:05.37,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.02,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:08.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.55,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you? You suddenly spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:14.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:26.78,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.84,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Do you feel ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:32.60,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.38,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.61,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Subaru-kun... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.78,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.28,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Not in front of my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.89,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.70,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.71,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure there's {\i1}nyo{\i0}thing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:59.05,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds are one thing, but there's \N{\i1}nyo{\i0} helping his mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:01.53,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell how this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.68,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've checked every inch of him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.44,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,What are the odds of it being a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:11.26,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,There's {\i1}nyo{\i0} indication of any \Ninterference using mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.72,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If Felis is unable to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:19.44,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,no one in this household can heal him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.73,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.53,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot thank you enough \Nfor your generous concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.76,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. There's no mana interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:30.74,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.55,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The witch's miasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,In my master's stead, I thank you \Nfor your kindness during our stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Give Emilia this message, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:51.51,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,"Let us compete in a manner that \Nwill bring neither of us shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.89,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:58.11,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,I know why you're returning to the mansion, \Nbut can anyone there heal him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.92,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,He utters our names, only occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.93,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,My name, my sister's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:07.66,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And Emilia-sama's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.12,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.54,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,maybe his condition will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:17.25,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I realize this is tasteless, but I must ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:21.58,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,How can you give so much of \Nyourself for Natsuki Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:27.26,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with him is not that of \Nmaster and servant, like Felis and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:28.93,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.85,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,your behavior and the glances you \Ncast are those a woman gives a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.23,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry. Forget I said—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.81,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It is... How can I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.78,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:54.37,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it is because Subaru-kun is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.88,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.12,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was stunned speechless for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.96,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru is a lucky man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.45,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:11.39,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,If he ever recovers, I'll have \Nto tease him to the max!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.68,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.88,Default,Felix,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:41.34,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know I mustn't let my personal \Nfeelings interfere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to keep you to myself at Crusch-sama's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.55,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do that at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.75,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I knew that something \Nwas troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:03.89,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I heard that you'd \Nquarreled with Emilia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.86,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll be all right, Subaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:11.49,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are always...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.24,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,fanatical like a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,And you're a remarkable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.30,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.34,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That was Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.60,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I must return quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Do not touch Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.15,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Witch cultists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:29.02,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Huma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.75,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.99,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.25,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.59,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You stole my sister's horn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:52.63,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and stole my reason to live, \Nbut that wasn't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:58.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have come here, and steal \Nmy reason to die, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:19.89,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:23.12,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:28.35,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't happen to be Pride, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.32,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're not going to answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.19,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't introduced myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.03,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,In the Witch's Cult, I am a Sin Archbishop
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,representing sloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:59.03,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how comical...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:12.29,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,What a very, very, very, very, \Nvery entertaining sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:15.45,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, truly, truly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.80,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My brain trembles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.78,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what has brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.73,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon-drawn carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, aren't ground dragons great?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,They obey diligently, work diligently,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:35.40,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,and play their role as a species diligently! \NThey're just fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:38.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.10,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:44.83,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Your diligence brought the ground dragon, \Ndiligence itself, to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:47.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my brain trembles, trembles, trembles,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:50.93,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,trembles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:56.04,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,But a dead ground dragon is the \Nvery definition of "sloth."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.00,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up the area at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:05.35,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,With the day of the Ordeal upon us, we \Nmustn't allow our existence to be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.68,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,And his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:08.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Unknown...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.28,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It is unknown if the girl is alive or dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.61,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Unknown if she is alive or dead, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:18.61,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly slothful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.70,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,With the forthcoming Ordeal, \Nyou let a potential problem remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.27,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the sincerity you show \Nin return for our Gospel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.33,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Sloth, sloth, sloth, sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:36.84,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us the sloth that has \Nled us to betray your goodwill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.05,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Love... We must repay love with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.44,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.18,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,If she lives, kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.33,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,If not, bring me her head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:51.56,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Love! We must repay love with love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.03,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.29,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.66,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You will look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.75,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. Answer me carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:21.92,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why does such dense love hang, \Nso abundant, upon your person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.97,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not own a copy of the Gospel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:31.27,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It saddens me to be ignored!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.44,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm treating you so kindly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet, and yet, and yet, and yet, \Nyet, yet, yet, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.59,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I will change the \Norder of my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.36,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.53,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.79,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,pretend that your mind has broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.90,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.21,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I truly have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.64,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why and for what reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for what purpose, do you act crazed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.30,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Your insanity is far too sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.98,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,To behave so cleverly and quietly, \Nas if seeking sympathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:20.98,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It is an insult to real madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:27.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You are a poorly-acted madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:31.91,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,If you really meant it, you would \Npay the gazes of others no heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:38.46,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, how comical! How comical!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.59,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I pity you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.26,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I pity your wretched, ugly, lowly, \Ndiminutive, sinful being,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:53.68,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all that, you are so loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:58.77,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You'd rather waste away in stagnation than \Nrepay the goodwill shown to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:10.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly slothful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:11.99,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.75,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:25.88,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.14,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,How fantastic this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:35.75,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, a lone girl, is badly injured. \NBut still, she presses on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.35,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your nonsense, witch worshiper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.70,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,To carry out your insubordinate acts
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.86,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,in Roswaal-sama's domain, \Nwithout permission, you are fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:48.96,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,In my absent master's stead, I, Rem, \Nshall carry out the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.74,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,In your battered state?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:56.48,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You have only come here to retrieve this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:59.41,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop saying things \Nthat merely sound attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.33,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.59,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.69,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:10.79,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,That shout was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:13.44,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Why does a believer in love, such as yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,adhere to someone like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.58,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You know nothing about Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.26,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,El Huma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:25.52,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic... That was fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.67,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,My brain trembles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.18,Default - italics,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Authority of Sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.74,Default - italics,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Unseen Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.89,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Look. You must look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.83,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,That is the result of your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:07.36,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,By doing nothing, you practiced sloth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:10.72,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, the girl is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.57,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.83,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,How awful! How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:17.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.40,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,With my arm, with my fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:25.30,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You... You... You... You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.84,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,killed her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:30.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,—op it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.44,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:36.51,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.47,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.19,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:51.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:56.41,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:59.16,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I finally got you to call me by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.41,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.45,Default,Suabru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.97,Default,Suabru,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.05,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,This place is quite the mess now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.92,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll just leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.60,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men! You will resume your duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.93,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Rendezvous with the other fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.14,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,The Ordeal will proceed as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.06,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Now, as for your position in all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bastard! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.10,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly have no idea what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:32.57,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,so I shall judge you as our Lord sees fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:32.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.07,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave you bound here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.78,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Should the Gospel happen\Nto find its way to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.82,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure you will be saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:48.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! I'll kill you! I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.33,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.25,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you are also a believer in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.25,0:17:57.36,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you sacrificed yourself for love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,defying your own fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.66,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,But you fell before your\Nfeelings reached him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.44,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,and your love had nowhere to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.85,Default,Betel,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly slothful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:14.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!\NI'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:31.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you. I'll kill you. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you... I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:38.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you. I'll kill you.\NI'll kill you. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:52.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:06.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem... Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.88,0:19:09.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem... Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem! Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:24.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem... Hey, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.47,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Hu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:27.84,Default - italics,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,...ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:37.03,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:40.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem... Wait, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.42,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:55.05,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Love... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:19:59.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:20:59.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:24.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:39.56,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.28,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Along with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:20.08,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0060,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:22.66,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:23.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:24.88,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?\NYou suddenly spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:29.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:30.76,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:32.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.51,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.56,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.64,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've seen a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.29,0:23:40.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:42.95,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:45.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:45.84,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:47.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:48.94,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:51.42,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to interrupt when you're \Njust getting heated up,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:54.41,Default,Kadomon,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't run my business with \Nyou two flirting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.25,0:23:58.29,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-kun, can I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:23:59.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.78,0:24:03.19,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I may be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.25,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:08.96,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The unpleasant smell on you seems \Nto have grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Unpleasant smell, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:17.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if you're worried, keep hold of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:17.85,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.31,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This feels a lot safer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.15,0:24:22.77,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.78,0:24:35.82,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Outside of {\c&H5AAD33&}Mad{\c&HFFFFFF&}ness
